SUMMARY:Deadline: America On Tech: Tech Flex Leaders Program
DESCRIPTION:America On Tech's Tech Flex Leaders Program is open to young pe
 ople interested in tech who are curious\, resourceful\, and ready to build
  something new. No prior tech experience is required. Participants earn an
  America On Tech certificate and receive a USD 500 stipend for completing 
 the program. WHO IT'S FOR: young people interested in tech\; no prior tech
  experience required. AWARD: USD 500 stipend plus certificate. DEADLINE: 5
  July 2026 priority\, open until 17 August 2026. TO APPLY: submit the appl
 ication via the America On Tech program page.\n\nOrganisation: America On 
 Tech\nLocation: United States. Remote/hybrid program.\nAward: USD 500 stip
 end on completion\, plus an America On Tech certificate. No application fe
 e.\nDuration: Program cohort (dates per program).\n\nMore: https://america
 ontech.org/tech-flex-leaders.html?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&ut
 m_medium=referral
